snippet.title: Super Code Strike available on iOS
snippet.description:
Design and create your own games with Super Code Strike! Play solo or multiplayer to connect with friends. Hack in-game elements with blockly coding. Strike other players’ islands to climb the leaderboards and collect coins to unlock customizations and new building items! NOW AVAIlABLE in Early Access, on iOS within Canada!
